</pre> app_package.to_files(temp_dir.name)  !cat $TMP_APP_DIR/schemas/$APP_NAME.sd <pre>schema myschema {
    document myschema {
        field id type string {
            indexing: attribute | summary
        }
        field title type string {
            indexing: index | summary
            index: enable-bm25
        }
        field body type string {
            indexing: index | summary
            index: enable-bm25
        }
    }
    fieldset default {
        fields: title, body
    }
    rank-profile default {
        first-phase {
            expression {
                bm25(title) + bm25(body)
            }
        }
    }
}</pre> In [54]: Copied! <pre>!cat $TMP_APP_DIR/services.xml
